	if {Lifesteal} is "Disabled":
		send "&7[ &4Exception Occurred &7] &cLifesteal is disabled. (Lifesteal)" to player			

on place:
	if {Item.Heart::*} contains player's held item:
		cancel event
	if {Item.Heart::*} contains player's off hand item:
		cancel event

